data.description: Welcome to this updated (2020) 4 bed, 2 bath ranch nestled in the charming Roosevelt Gardens neighborhood! This gem boasts an inviting open floor plan for both relaxing and entertaining. The spacious kitchen showcases a large bar counter, great for casual dining or gathering with loved ones. Step outside onto the rebuilt deck and into the fenced backyard, where you'll find ample space that would be wonderful for outdoor enjoyment and activities. This well-kept home is ready for you to make it your own and create lasting memories. Currently occupied by a tenant paying $1600 per month, providing an excellent opportunity for investors or those looking to offset mortgage costs. Lease is up in April, offering flexibility for occupancy. Don't miss out on the chance to call this delightful property home sweet home! Schedule your showing today and seize the opportunity to make this your own slice of paradise in Roosevelt Gardens.
